sidebar:
  order: 2
---

import { Tabs, TabItem } from '$lib/mdx';

Gerencie repositórios pela Management API. Requer autenticação JWT.

---

## Criar Repositório

### POST /api/v1/management/databases/\{databaseId\}/repositories

Cria um novo repositório em um banco de dados.

**Request:**
```json
{
  "name": "companies",
  "entityName": "Company",
  "schema": {
    "name": { "type": "string", "required": true },
    "industry": { "type": "string", "required": false },
    "employeeCount": { "type": "number", "required": false }
  }
}
```

| Campo | Tipo | Obrigatório | Descrição |
|-------|------|----------|-------------|
| `name` | string | Sim | Nome do repositório |
| `entityName` | string | Sim | Nome do tipo de entidade |
| `schema` | object | Não | Definição de schema para validação |

**Response (201 Created):**
```json
{
  "repositoryId": "repo_abc123",
  "databaseId": "db_abc123",
  "name": "companies",
  "entityName": "Company",
  "createdAt": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z"
}
```

---

## Listar Repositórios

### GET /api/v1/management/databases/\{databaseId\}/repositories

Lista todos os repositórios em um banco de dados.

**Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
  "repositories": [
    {
      "repositoryId": "repo_abc123",
      "databaseId": "db_abc123",
      "name": "companies",
      "entityName": "Company",
      "status": "Active",
      "schema": {
        "name": { "type": "string", "required": true }
      },
      "itemCount": 500,
      "createdAt": "2024-01-15T10:00:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "nextCursor": null
}
```

---

## Obter Repositório

### GET /api/v1/management/databases/\{databaseId\}/repositories/\{repositoryId\}

Obtém um repositório específico por ID.

**Response (200 OK):** Mesmo formato do repositório individual na resposta de listagem.

---

## Excluir Repositório

### DELETE /api/v1/management/databases/\{databaseId\}/repositories/\{repositoryId\}

Exclui um repositório e todas as suas entidades.

:::caution[Aviso]
Isso exclui permanentemente o repositório e todos os seus dados.
:::

**Response (204 No Content):** Corpo vazio em caso de sucesso.

---

## Definição de Schema

Defina schemas para validação de entidades:
```json
{
  "schema": {
    "name": {
      "type": "string",
      "required": true,
      "minLength": 1,
      "maxLength": 100
    },
    "email": {
      "type": "string",
      "required": true,
      "pattern": "^[^@]+@[^@]+\\.[^@]+$"
    },
    "age": {
      "type": "number",
      "required": false,
      "min": 0,
      "max": 150
    },
    "isActive": {
      "type": "boolean",
      "required": false,
      "default": true
    },
    "tags": {
      "type": "array",
      "required": false,
      "items": { "type": "string" }
    }
  }
}
```

### Tipos de Campo do Schema

| Tipo | Descrição | Opções de Validação |
|------|-------------|-------------------|
| `string` | Valor de texto | `minLength`, `maxLength`, `pattern` |
| `number` | Valor numérico | `min`, `max` |
| `boolean` | True/false | - |
| `array` | Lista de valores | `items`, `minItems`, `maxItems` |
| `object` | Objeto aninhado | `properties` |

---

## Exemplos de Código

<Tabs items={[{"label":"C# SDK","content":"<pre><code class=\"language-csharp\">    // Create repository\n    var createResult = await client.Repositories.CreateAsync(\n        &quot;db_abc123&quot;,\n        new CreateRepositoryRequest(\n            Name: &quot;customers&quot;,\n            EntityName: &quot;Customer&quot;,\n            Schema: new Dictionary&lt;string, SchemaField&gt;\n            {\n                [&quot;name&quot;] = new() { Type = &quot;string&quot;, Required = true },\n                [&quot;email&quot;] = new() { Type = &quot;string&quot;, Required = true },\n                [&quot;tier&quot;] = new() { Type = &quot;string&quot;, Required = false }\n            }\n        )\n    );\n\n    // List repositories\n    var listResult = await client.Repositories.ListAsync(&quot;db_abc123&quot;);\n\n    foreach (var repo in listResult.Value.Repositories)\n    {\n        Console.WriteLine($&quot;{repo.Name} ({repo.EntityName}): {repo.ItemCount} items&quot;);\n    }\n\n    // Get repository\n    var repoResult = await client.Repositories.GetAsync(&quot;db_abc123&quot;, &quot;repo_abc123&quot;);\n\n    // Delete repository\n    var deleteResult = await client.Repositories.DeleteAsync(&quot;db_abc123&quot;, &quot;repo_abc123&quot;);\n</code></pre>"},{"label":"cURL","content":"<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">    # Create repository\n    curl -X POST &quot;https://api.terrascale.io/api/v1/management/databases/db_abc123/repositories&quot; \\\n      -H &quot;Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGci...&quot; \\\n      -H &quot;Content-Type: application/json&quot; \\\n      -d &#39;{\n        &quot;name&quot;: &quot;customers&quot;,\n        &quot;entityName&quot;: &quot;Customer&quot;,\n        &quot;schema&quot;: {\n          &quot;name&quot;: { &quot;type&quot;: &quot;string&quot;, &quot;required&quot;: true },\n          &quot;email&quot;: { &quot;type&quot;: &quot;string&quot;, &quot;required&quot;: true }\n        }\n      }&#39;\n\n    # List repositories\n    curl &quot;https://api.terrascale.io/api/v1/management/databases/db_abc123/repositories&quot; \\\n      -H &quot;Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGci...&quot;\n\n    # Delete repository\n    curl -X DELETE &quot;https://api.terrascale.io/api/v1/management/databases/db_abc123/repositories/repo_abc123&quot; \\\n      -H &quot;Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGci...&quot;\n</code></pre>"}]} />

